# Agentic Hemispheres — Cursor Template

**Authoritative rules** live in [`.cursor/rules/`](.cursor/rules/) (especially `03_callosum.mdc`, `06_ai_navigation.mdc`). This file is a short pointer so the template stays maintainable—avoid duplicating full handshake JSON here.

## In one minute

- **Master:** high-reasoning model from [`.cursor/models.json`](.cursor/models.json) → `master`.
- **Emissary:** implementer subagent ([`.cursor/agents/implementer.md`](.cursor/agents/implementer.md)); **Verifier:** [`verifier.md`](.cursor/agents/verifier.md). Subagents do not nest.
- **Transport:** JSON handshakes + [`.cursor/plans/workspace_state.json`](.cursor/plans/workspace_state.json) with `schema_version` — see Corpus Callosum rule.
- **Hooks:** [`.cursor/hooks.json`](.cursor/hooks.json) runs post-edit validation via [`scripts/cursor-after-file-edit.mjs`](scripts/cursor-after-file-edit.mjs).

## Docs

- [docs/MAP.md](docs/MAP.md) — start here.
- [docs/cursor3-agents-playbook.md](docs/cursor3-agents-playbook.md) — Cursor 3 Agents Window, worktrees, `/best-of-n`, `Await`.

**Template version:** see `TEMPLATE_VERSION` in [README.md](README.md).
